      "text": "バンド曲のカバーということで、初めは\n愛ちゃんすずにゃんとうんうん唸ってたんですけど",
      "startTime": 15.7737876574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.9716571888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "放課後ティータイムのみなさんと長電話したら、曲の\n空気感が見えてきて……振り付けまで浮かんだんです",
      "startTime": 22.307122008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.4678698939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "「フェスに出演する高校生とコラボする」と聞いた時は\n驚いたけど、なんとかなりそうで良かったよ",
      "startTime": 30.2666683833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.9345364017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "勢いでコラボを決めちゃいましたけど……\n大丈夫でしたか？",
      "startTime": 36.9844917297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "先方に確認したら「それは面白い！」と大喜びだったよ\n心置きなくやってくれ",
      "startTime": 44.0000017166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9230621896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか！　ふふふ、任せて下さい！\nこころ達がどーんと盛り上げてみせますから！",
      "startTime": 49.3978930473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8171883506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "楽しみにしてるよ\n他に何か気になったことはないか？",
      "startTime": 54.800001208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
